Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Calls a function on an entity's script object

Usage
-----

*void* callFunction( *string* **functionName** )

Parameters
----------

-   [functionName] - The name of the function to call.

Examples
--------

    Â 
    $my_entity.callFunction("fire");

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values.

Also see [hasFunction](HasFunction_%28script_event%29 "HasFunction (script event)") .


